PROJECT CONTEXT

GARIMPO IA is a SaaS platform designed to discover auction opportunities, analyze them with AI, assign a score (0-100), and alert users about profitable assets.

The system aims to become a large-scale intelligence platform for physical assets (similar to Bloomberg but for auctions and real-world assets).

Current stack:

Frontend
- React 19
- Vite
- TypeScript
- Tailwind

Backend
- Supabase (Auth + PostgreSQL + RLS)
- Edge Functions

AI
- Google Gemini

Payments
- Stripe subscriptions

Core features implemented include:

- opportunity feed
- opportunity detail page
- AI scoring pipeline
- alert rules
- notifications
- watchlist
- analytics dashboard
- admin opportunity insertion
- automated scraping architecture
- ingestion pipeline
- duplicate detection
- monitoring and logging
- scheduled scrapers

